RelatedSentence: CHENNAI : The model code of conduct that was in force since the announcement of Lok Sabha elections on March 5 ceased to be in operation after Chief Election Commissioner V S Sampath presented the list of new MPs to President Pranab Mukherjee on Sunday evening , according to a statement from Tamil Nadu chief electoral officer Praveen Kumar .
